## Interface: 30300
## Title: COA Guardian Plates
## Notes: Suppresses friendly PLAYER nameplates while leaving friendly guardian/pet/NPC nameplates visible, whenever the native Friendly Nameplates option shows them. Also offers an optional tri-state threat-coloring capability for enemy nameplates. Low-risk theorycraft companion addon for Conquest of Azeroth.
